6度纬度
Six degrees latitude.

657
01:09:42,656 --> 01:09:45,606
离复活岛差了十万八千里
Not one mile closer to Easter Island.

658
01:09:50,906 --> 01:09:52,576
我们被诅咒了
We are cursed.

659
01:09:52,746 --> 01:09:55,706
当我们赶上风带我们会弥补上的
We'll make up for it when we catch the variables.

660
01:09:58,686 --> 01:10:00,216
我们会赶上的
We'll catch 'em.

661
01:10:35,356 --> 01:10:36,506
