<i>Mr. Joy, the halyard's jammed.

663
01:10:47,976 --> 01:10:51,356
<i>花花公子 抓住它 花花公子
<i>Mr. Joy! Grab at it, Mr. Joy!

664
01:10:57,946 --> 01:10:59,766
<i>马修
<i>Matthew!

665
